Select      ISQBW.[Depo AdÄ±], ISQBW.TransactionTypeId, ISQBW.TransactionTypeCode, ISQBW.ItemId, ISQBW.LotId, ISQBW.SerieId
          , *
From        dbo.Pv_Rn_Inventory_BillItemSeries ISQBW
Where         ISQBW.SerieId = 90083
Order By    ISQBW.AddDate


Select      ITILA.TransactionDate, ITILA.AddDate, ITILA.TransactionTypeId, ITILA.TransactionTypeCode, ITILA.WarehouseName
          , ITILA.ItemId, ITILA.LotId, ITILA.SerieId, ITILA.Quantity, ITILA.BillId, *
From        dbo.Pv_Rn_Inventory_TransactionItemLotAnalysis ITILA
Where         ITILA.WarehouseId = 160 And ITILA.SerieId = 90083
Order By    ITILA.AddDate
Go 


Select  TFRISQBWAO.WarehouseId, TFRISQBWAO.ItemId, TFRISQBWAO.LotId, TFRISQBWAO.SerieId, TFRISQBWAO.TotalQuantity, *
From    dbo.TvFn_Rn_Inventory_SeriesQuantityByWarehouse_AsOf(GETDATE()) TFRISQBWAO
